# AIB ERP Monorepo Architecture Directives

## 1. Global Project Layout
- **Frontend Core & API Handlers**: `/apps/web` (Next.js with TypeScript & Tailwind CSS)
- **Shared Data Layer Models**: `/packages/database`

## 2. Technical Strategy Rules
- **Language Uniformity**: All frontend interfaces and server-side routines must be authored strictly in **TypeScript**.
- **Database Engine Rules**: All relational maps reference `packages/database/schema.sql`. You must never write queries or data scripts that bypass PostgreSQL Row Level Security (RLS) policies. Every operation must isolate by a valid `tenant_id`.
- **UX Constraint**: Raw HTML or un-mapped Tailwind utility declarations for base buttons or tables are strictly prohibited. centralize through a uniform element kit.